ry 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "2982", "end_offset": "3025", "annotation_id": "GE_033"}, {"decision": "Again demonstrated is a right-sided hydronephrosis with a soft tissue density surrounding the right mid ureter just cephalad to the sacral promontory. Delayed excretion is again identified as on prior study.", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "3027", "end_offset": "3234", "annotation_id": "GE_034"}, {"decision": "Soft tissue thickening is again demonstrated within the duodenum, however given lack of oral contrast, specific comparison is difficult. ", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "3237", "end_offset": "3374", "annotation_id": "GE_035"}, {"decision": "There are multiple fluid filled and mildly dilated loops of small bowel. The terminal ileum is collapsed.", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "3374", "end_offset": "3479", "annotation_id": "GE_036"}, {"decision": "Grouped small bowel loops make identification of a discrete transition point difficult", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "3480", "end_offset": "3566", "annotation_id": "GE_037"}, {"decision": "The colon contains air and stool extending all the way to the colostomy site within the left lower quadrant. ", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "3568", "end_offset": "3677", "annotation_id": "GE_038"}, {"decision": "There is wide-mouth parastomal hernia with no evidence of incarceration as on prior study. There are multiple omental metastatic lesions as demonstrated on prior study similar in size.", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "3677", "end_offset": "3861", "annotation_id": "GE_039"}, {"decision": "CT PELVIS WITH IV CONTRAST", "category": "Category 6: Therapeutic procedure related", "start_offset": "3864", "end_offset": "3890", "annotation_id": "GE_040"}, {"decision": "The urinary bladder is unremarkab